 brackets.\", \"from\": 7827, \"to\": 8001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7868, \"end\": 7874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9980204325170255, \"rank\": 0.0013506997035948802, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7883, \"end\": 7896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9926590224782484, \"rank\": 0.0070110980498355084, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7914, \"end\": 7920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9933482310902005, \"rank\": 0.006291198077851166, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Benesh and Partain are the only Americans left; they play Qatar, the Tokyo bronze medalists, in the second set of quarterfinals on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 8002, \"to\": 8143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8060, \"end\": 8065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8926801875105465, \"rank\": 0.12022120864208635, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8071, \"end\": 8076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"