mpics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The levels are getting better each time.\", \"from\": 8404, \"to\": 8445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone is investing in the sport.\", \"from\": 8446, \"to\": 8481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of people came to Brazil to study beach volleyball,\\\" Evandro said, noting that of the 24 teams in the men's field, 23 of them had won on the world tour.\", \"from\": 8482, \"to\": 8640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8506, \"end\": 8512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9980204325170255, \"rank\": 0.0013506997035948802, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8541, \"end\": 8548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evandro_Guerra\", \"score\": 0.9999991288895372, \"rank\": 5.22647315356502e-07, \"text\": \"Evandro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evandro_Guerra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evandro_Guerra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today there are no favorites in this game.\", \"from\": 8641, \"to\": 8684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are talking about an Olympics, everyone can lose and everyone can win.\", \"from\": 8685, \"to\": 8758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The level today is really hard.\\\"\", \"from\": 8759, \"to\": 8791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ana Patricia and Duda play Latvia on Wednesday, hoping to avoid Brazil's second shutout ever- and second in a row.\", \"from\": 8793, \"to\": 8907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8797, \"end\": 8805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patricia_Arquette\", \"score\": 0.9999999329888873, \"rank\": 6.